  "page": "Battle of Bitter River",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of Bitter River</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bitter_River\" title=\"Bitter River\">Bitter River</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Blackwood.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/45px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/60px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a>\n</p>\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Bracken.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/45px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/60px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Blackwood.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">Blackwood</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Bracken.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/20px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/40px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">Bracken</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      777 <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a><br />7 <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septons</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of Bitter River</b> was a great battle fought at the <a href=\"/index.php/Bitter_River\" title=\"Bitter River\">Bitter River</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Bitter_River&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">Blackwood</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">Bracken</a>, ancient rivals, allied together to oppose the invading <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a>. According to song, the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> were shattered by 777 charging Andal <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a>, who were accompanied by seven <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septons</a>, as seven is a holy number in the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The Brackens converted to the Faith while the Blackwoods remained loyal to the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">old gods</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Bitter_River&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">So Spake Martin: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Blackwood_Bracken_Feud_and_Coinage\">Blackwood-Bracken Feud and Coinage</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404202440\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.050 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.188 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 223/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9105/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6981/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 812/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 946/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.16 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  176.942      1 -total\n 96.20%  170.218      1 Template:Battlebox\n 95.83%  169.559      1 Template:Infobox\n  2.54%    4.502      1 Template:Ref\n  1.48%    2.610      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.95%    1.686      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18920-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404202440 an